Silvana Koch-Mehrin, a German Free
Democratic Party lawmaker and a member of the European
Parliament, resigned from all political offices following
accusations of plagiarism concerning her doctoral thesis,
 Handelsblatt  newspaper reported, citing a statement by Koch-
